      "isLeaf": true,
      "summary": "\n\n**單調棧與矩形**：\n- 柱狀圖最大矩形：維護遞增棧，彈出時計算面積\n- 最大矩形（2D）：逐行計算高度，轉化為柱狀圖問題\n- 接雨水：單調棧計算每個凹槽能接的水量\n\n```cpp\n// 柱狀圖中最大矩形\nint largestRectangleArea(vector<int>& heights) {\n    int n = heights.size(), ans = 0;\n    stack<int> st;\n    for (int i = 0; i <= n; ++i) {\n        int h = (i == n) ? 0 : heights[i]; // 末尾加哨兵 0 清空棧\n        while (!st.empty() && heights[st.top()] > h) {\n            int height = heights[st.top()];\n            st.pop();\n            int width = st.empty() ? i : (i - st.top() - 1); // 計算矩形寬度\n            ans = max(ans, height * width);\n        }\n        st.push(i);\n    }\n    return ans;\n}\n```"
